QuestData.Title: Quelling Causalities
QuestData.Description:
The Infinite has forced the energies of time to aggression. This is not good.
Please slay any time elementals you encounter while assisting Ambassador Chronormu. I will remain here and help her hold Eternus in place.
QuestData.RewardText: Excellent work! Usually I am against killing time, but today is an exception.
